description: MaxFastigheter i Sverige AB engages in the ownership, development, and management of commercial properties. The company is headquartered in Torshaella, Sodermanlands and currently employs 9 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-06-29. The firm owns, manages and develops commercial properties. The firm's property portfolio consists of commercial properties located on various local venues in Sweden, such as Avesta, Eskilstuna, Fagersta, Karlstad, Norrkoping, Sandsvall, Vasteras, Osthammar. Its property portfolio's leasable area is approximately 70,000 sqm.
name: MaxFastigheter i Sverige AB
